  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to <span class=\"text-highlight\">200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Peel</span> and finely chop the&nbsp;<strong>brown&nbsp;onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong>&nbsp;olive oil</strong> over&nbsp;a medium heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the<strong> ground</strong>&nbsp;<strong>cumin</strong> and <strong>smoked&nbsp;paprika</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the <strong>sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>black beans</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>black beans</strong> to the pan&nbsp;with the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong></p>\r\n<p>Crumble in the&nbsp;<strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong><span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;</span>and cook for a further 5 min, stirring until everything's combined <span class=\"text-highlight\">&ndash;</span> these are your <strong>Mexican beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
