          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1427.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, lightly grease an <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>oven-proof dish</strong></span> with <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once the <strong>Mexican beans </strong>are&nbsp;done, add&nbsp;<span class=\"text-highlight\">1/3</span> of them to&nbsp;the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>oven-proof dish</strong></span> and top<span class=\"text-highlight\"> the beans</span> with 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4]</span> <strong>tortillas</strong>&nbsp;</p>",
